  "detailed_description": "Hexanome is a turn-based puzzle game. It's a sequel to the previous game Hexa Turn. This time you play as a triangle and AI tries to stop you.<br><br>Pick your next move carefully in order to collect all squares and outsmart the AI.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/956010/extras/5a9bcb1b22d7890d81c130fc74b3b714.poster.avif?t=1638015785\" width=400 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/956010/extras/5a9bcb1b22d7890d81c130fc74b3b714.webm?t=1638015785\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/956010/extras/5a9bcb1b22d7890d81c130fc74b3b714.mp4?t=1638015785\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Hexanome contains 76 fresh and challenging puzzles.<br>Can you outsmart the AI again?<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Clever puzzle experience<br></li><li> Carefully crafted 76 unique levels<br></li><li> Beautifully designed minimalist visuals<br></li><li> Calming music and sound effects<br></li><li> 14 Steam achievements</li></ul>",
